# FilledColumn.WrappedElement

**Type Alias**

The type of the column’s elements that defines an associated type for the optional column protocol.

## Declaration

```swift
typealias WrappedElement = Base.WrappedElement
```

## Discussion

See [doc://com.apple.TabularData/documentation/TabularData/OptionalColumnProtocol] for more information.

## Supporting Types

- **FilledColumn.Element**: The type of the column’s elements that defines an associated type for the bidirectional collection protocol.
